Puppet module: varnish

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages varnish software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include varnish              # Install and run varnish with standard configurations.
include varnish::disable     # Disable varnish service.
include varnish::disableboot # Disable varnish service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include varnish::absent      # Remove varnish package.

DEPENDENCIES:
